          "headersSize": 573,
          "httpVersion": "HTTP/1.1",
          "method": "POST",
          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"output\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"topic\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"summary\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"topic\",\"summary\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}}},\"required\":[\"output\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"\\n    <background>\\n      The user and agent have been brainstorming about their business idea.\\n    </background>\\n\\n    <available_topics>\\n      \\\"idea: The core business idea. What does the business do? What makes them different?\\\", \\\"audience: The target audience. What are their pain points? What are their goals?\\\", \\\"solution: How does the user's business solve the audience's pain points, or help them reach their goals?\\\", \\\"socialProof: Social proof or testimonials to include on the landing page. Remember, anything can be social proof: the user's background, experience, beliefs, founder story, etc.\\\", \\\"lookAndFeel: The look and feel of the landing page.\\\"\\n    </available_topics>\\n\\n    <task>\\n      Read the recent chat history, and summarize their answers,\\n      preserving as much information as possible. This will be used to generate \\n      persuasive marketing copy, so be sure to capture all the details.\\n\\n      If the user has answered MULTIPLE topics well, return an array of objects with the following shape:\\n      {\\n          topic: string,\\n          summary: string,\\n      }\\n    </task>\\n    \\n    <chat-history>\\n  <message>... 2 more messages...</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"What is your business?\\\"</message>\\n  <message>human: \\\"Friend of the Pod is a podcast matchmaking service.\\\\n            We help both sides: hosts get great content, guests get exposure,\\\\n            and we're the only platform that does this at scale.\\\\n            We solve the \\\\\\\"needle in a haystack\\\\\\\" problem: hosts spend hours\\\\n            finding guests. We do it in minutes with AI-powered filtering.\\\"</message>\\n</chat-history>\\n\\n    <output>\\n      Return an array of objects with the following shape:\\n      {\\n          topic: string,\\n          summary: string,\\n      }\\n    </output>\\n  \"}]}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1547,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1547,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01GQ8sEkLPyWEVgmiDkzXmTB\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_015Ko9HFq2hUkVjhvxgSeE2S\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"output\":[{\"topic\":\"idea\",\"summary\":\"Friend of the Pod is a podcast matchmaking service that connects podcast hosts with guests. They differentiate themselves by being the only platform that does this at scale, using AI-powered filtering to solve the 'needle in a haystack' problem. They serve both sides of the market: hosts get great content and guests get exposure.\"},{\"topic\":\"solution\",\"summary\":\"The business solves the time-consuming problem of finding the right podcast guests. Hosts typically spend hours searching for suitable guests, but Friend of the Pod reduces this to minutes using AI-powered filtering technology. This saves hosts significant time while ensuring quality matches between hosts and guests.\"},{\"topic\":\"audience\",\"summary\":\"The target audience includes two groups: podcast hosts who need quality guests for their shows, and potential guests seeking exposure. The main pain point for hosts is the time-intensive process of finding suitable guests (the 'needle in a haystack' problem). Guests' goal is to gain exposure through podcast appearances.\"}]}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1158,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":281,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
          },
